---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Jephthah"
  description="Jephthah — founder-engineer in Abuja, building AI-native products solo."
>
  <section class="relative pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-32 md:pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-10">
      <span class="eyebrow text-muted-foreground">ABOUT / 2026</span>
      <h1
        class="font-display mt-6 max-w-5xl text-foreground"
        style="font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 9vw, 9rem); letter-spacing: -0.045em; line-height: 0.9;"
      >
        Founder-engineer.<br />
        <span style="color: var(--accent)">Abuja</span>, working globally.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative border-t border-border pt-16 pb-24 md:pt-24 md:pb-32">
    <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-[1440px] grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 px-6 md:gap-x-10 md:px-10">
      {/* Side rail */}
      <aside class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3">
        <dl class="space-y-8 md:sticky md:top-32">
          <div>
            <dt class="eyebrow text-muted-foreground">Currently</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-foreground">Abuja, Nigeria</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="eyebrow text-muted-foreground">Building</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-foreground">
              <div>DeeepSolve</div>
              <div>TrackQR</div>
              <div>ComplyNG</div>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="eyebrow text-muted-foreground">Available for</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-foreground">
              Founder-engineer roles,<br />AI-native product builds,<br />serious collaboration.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="eyebrow text-muted-foreground">CV</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <a
                href="/jephthah-cv.pdf"
                download
                class="eyebrow inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-foreground/40 pb-1 text-foreground transition-colors hover:border-foreground"
              >
                Download
                <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
              </a>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>

      {/* Body column */}
      <article
        class="col-span-12 mt-12 max-w-[65ch] text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5 md:mt-0 md:text-xl"
      >
        <p>
          I design, build, deploy, and operate software end-to-end. Most of what I ship is
          AI-native — products where the model is part of the runtime, not a bolt-on.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-8">
          I work solo because the products I want to ship don't exist yet, and waiting for
          someone else to build them isn't a plan. Four products live: <a
            href="/work/deeepsolve"
            class="border-b border-foreground/30 hover:border-foreground">DeeepSolve</a
          > (50K+ Nigerian students), <a
            href="/work/track-qr"
            class="border-b border-foreground/30 hover:border-foreground">TrackQR</a
          > (1M+ scans served), <a
            href="/work/complyng"
            class="border-b border-foreground/30 hover:border-foreground">ComplyNG</a
          > (continuous compliance for Nigerian startups), and <a
            href="/work/incented"
            class="border-b border-foreground/30 hover:border-foreground">Incented</a
          > (Web3 coordination infrastructure).
        </p>

        {/* TODO: Jephthah to fill — long-form bio, journey, what I'm building toward */}
        <p
          class="mt-8 rounded-md border border-dashed border-border bg-muted/30 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground"
        >
          [Placeholder] More long-form to come here — the journey, the bet on Africa, what
          I'm building toward. Drop the copy in <code>src/pages/about.astro</code>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
